com.fda.ctp.services

Class EssbaseDataQueryApplicationService

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fda.ctp.services.EssbaseDataQueryApplicationService

  • @Service(value="essbaseQuerySampleApApplicationService")
 @PropertySource(value="classpath:essbase/essbase-db.properties")
public class EssbaseDataQueryApplicationService
extends java.lang.Object
    Data Query Example does the following: Signs on to essbase domain, Opens a cube view, Performs Retrieve, ZoomIn, ZoomOut, KeepOnly, RemoveOnly, Pivot, and Signs Off. In order for this sample to work in your environment, make sure to change the s_* variables make sure to edit the method performCubeViewOperation() accordingly.
    Version:
    1
    Author:
    Rohit Prabhu
